SubWizard Methods

Requires: VI Scripting

View the class hierarchy.

MethodDescription
Is Locked By MeReturns a value of TRUE if the object is in the SubWizard list of locked objects. Details
Lock ConstAdds a diagram constant to a SubWizard list of locked objects. Details
Lock ObjectAdds the specified object to the SubWizard list of locked objects. Details
Unlock ConstRemoves a diagram constant from a SubWizard list of locked objects Details
Unlock ObjectUnlocks panel objects. If the Objects parameter is not wired, the currently selected objects are unlocked. Details
